'''大夏巨龍屬'''（[[屬名|屬名]]：{{lang|la|''Daxiatitan''}}，意為「[[大夏河|大夏河]]的巨人」）是[[多孔椎龍類|多孔椎龍類]][[蜥腳下目|蜥腳]][[恐龍|恐龍]]的一個[[屬|屬]]，屬於基礎[[泰坦巨龍類|泰坦巨龍類]]或其中的[[盤足龍科|盤足龍科]]，化石來自[[中國|中國]]西北部[[甘肅省|甘肅省]]蘭州盆地的[[下白堊紀|下白堊紀]]地層，迄今已發現部分[[脊椎|脊椎]]、[[胸帶|肩帶]]和[[大腿骨|大腿骨]]<ref name=Youetal08>{{cite journal |last=You |first=H.-L. |author2=Li, D.-Q. |author3=Zhou, L.-Q. |author4=Ji, Q |year=2008 |title=''Daxiatitan binglingi'': a giant sauropod dinosaur from the Early Cretaceous of China |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/308546865_Daxiatitan_binglingi_a_giant_sauropod_dinosaur_from_the_Early_Cretaceous_of_China |journal=''Gansu Geology'' |volume=17 |issue=4 |pages=1–10 |issn=1004-4116 |access-date=2020-10-03 |archive-date=2020-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401115914/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/308546865_Daxiatitan_binglingi_a_giant_sauropod_dinosaur_from_the_Early_Cretaceous_of_China |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其全長估計可達23至30公尺，在亞洲恐龍中名列前茅<ref name=Youetal08/><ref name="Holtz2008">{{cite book | author = Holtz, T. R. Jr. | chapter = Dinosaur Genus List [Updated 13 January 2011] | title = ''Dinosaurs: The Most Complete, Up-to-Date Encyclopedia for Dinosaur Lovers of All Ages'' | publisher = Indiana University Press | isbn = 0-375-82419-7 | year = 2012 | chapter-url = http://www.geol.umd.edu/~tholtz/dinoappendix/HoltzappendixWinter2011.pdf | access-date = 2018-07-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170812011954/http://www.geol.umd.edu/~tholtz/dinoappendix/HoltzappendixWinter2011.pdf | archive-date = 2017-08-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>；而體重估計達23噸，和許多同等長度級的近親相比則顯小<ref name = Molina-Pérez>{{ cite book | author = Molina-Pérez, R.; Larramendi, A. | others = (譯) Donaghey, J. | title = 
''Dinosaur Facts and Figures: The Sauropods and Other Sauropodomorphs'' | publisher = [[Princeton_University_Press|Princeton University Press]] | year = 2020 | isbn = 978-0-691-19069-3 | pages = 123, 160, 262 }}</ref>。大夏巨龍具有極長的頸部，頸椎的大小在基礎泰坦巨龍類中也是數一數二，重建後的頸部可能超過12公尺，幾乎佔去全長的一半<ref name=Youetal08/><ref name = Molina-Pérez/>。
